{"tid":2348531,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解放軍進行演練 在香港附近海域防止「恐怖分子」從海上乘船外逃","createTime":"2020-12-31T18:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T03:32:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6336734698bdd0b40dc727eba0b8d82d294e8563","tid":2348531,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T18:12:42.000Z","msg":"深圳衞視昨播出的節目《直播港澳台》指，法院審理查明，偷渡船隻上所撿獲的衞星電話及涉案人員Telegram群組內訊息表明，鄧棨然及喬映瑜在「上家」的指揮下，策劃、組織自香港偷渡至台灣，鄧還負責購買偷渡所用船隻，並在「上家」的安排下，學習船隻基本駕駛技能。片段顯示，偷渡船為紅色及灰色船身的快艇，船體不大，連駕駛位置僅有數個座椅。<br />\n<br />\n另外， 據「央視軍事」報道，解放軍駐港部隊日前組織2020年度第四季度聯合海空巡邏，陸海空三軍部隊依托巡邏任務，展開叢林搜索、海上查證等多項實戰化課目演練。報道指演練在「香港某山地」舉行，事先通報了香港特區政府有關部門。特戰小組進行叢林清剿和搜捕工作後，海軍四艘艦艇與空軍兩架直升機出動，在香港附近海域進行警戒，防止「恐怖分子」從海上乘船外逃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210101/YRNO7GMF65FQBLXZRIIEMIBPDE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210101%2FYRNO7GMF65FQBLXZRIIEMIBPDE%2F&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=f04f6789\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210101%2FYRNO7GMF65FQBLXZRIIEMIBPDE%2F&h=f6547f3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210101/YRNO7GMF65FQBLXZRIIEMIBPDE/</a>"},{"pid":"d02061604ddab2ad33c0bd3395475bc131f0fa37","tid":2348531,"uid":126919,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T18:13:28.000Z","msg":"極速巴&hellip;新年平安快樂"},{"pid":"47378ee847cd9bcc513e36b677ddaf6db38f7e30","tid":2348531,"uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d02061604ddab2ad33c0bd3395475bc131f0fa37","tid":2348531,"uid":126919,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T18:13:28.000Z","msg":"極速巴&hellip;新年平安快樂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T18:17:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"h